# CMPE492-Design-and-Implementation-of-a-Robust-LLMOps-Platform Development Guidelines

Auto-generated from all feature plans. Last updated: 2026-04-16

## Active Technologies
- Python 3.11 (backend + frontend) + FastAPI 0.135, Pydantic 2.12, huggingface_hub 1.7, Streamlit 1.55, pytest, pytest-asyncio, httpx (006-session-persistence)
- In-memory backend session registry (process-local) + browser cookie-persisted session token for Streamlit client continuity; no database (006-session-persistence)
- SQLite file at `backend/data/llmops.db` (2 tables: `gcp_credentials`, `deployments`). Service-account JSON encrypted with Fernet; key read from `LLMOPS_ENCRYPTION_KEY` env var. (007-gke-inference-pipeline)

## Project Structure

```text
backend/
├── src/
│   ├── main.py                    # FastAPI app entry point
│   ├── api/
│   │   ├── auth.py                # POST /api/auth/verify, GET /api/auth/session, POST /api/auth/logout
│   │   ├── auth_helpers.py        # Shared session auth dependency
│   │   ├── deployment.py          # POST /api/deployment/mock (+ idempotency support)
│   │   ├── errors.py              # Global error handler
│   │   ├── models.py              # GET /api/models, GET /api/models/public (session-auth protected)
│   │   └── upload.py              # POST /api/upload/start (multi-folder, path sanitisation, idempotency)
│   ├── models/
│   │   ├── auth.py                # TokenVerifyResponse, SessionStatusResponse, LogoutResponse
│   │   ├── deployment.py
│   │   └── upload.py              # UploadStartResponse, FolderUploadResult, PublicModelInfoResponse
│   └── services/
│       ├── huggingface.py         # verify_hf_token, upload_model_folder, fetch_public_model_info, list_user_models
│       ├── mock_gcp.py
│       └── session_store.py       # In-memory session lifecycle + idempotency record store
└── tests/contract/
    ├── conftest.py                # Shared transport and session-store reset fixtures
    ├── test_auth_api.py
    ├── test_deployment_api.py
    ├── test_models_api.py         # Includes public model info tests (200/400/401/403/404)
    └── test_upload_api.py         # Includes multi-folder, path traversal, size limit, idempotency tests

frontend/
├── conftest.py                    # sys.path + session-state reset for pytest
├── src/
│   ├── app.py                     # Streamlit entry point — tabs: Upload, Select, Deploy
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── auth.py                # Login form
│   │   ├── deploy.py              # render_deployment_section, render_public_repo_deploy_section
│   │   └── upload.py              # Native directory picker + individual file uploader
│   └── services/
│       ├── api_client.py          # verify/get-session/logout, upload/list/fetch/deploy (+ idempotency headers)
│       └── session_client.py      # Streamlit session + browser cookie persistence sync
└── tests/integration/
    └── test_workflow.py           # End-to-end Streamlit AppTest tests (session restore + retry behaviors)
```

## Commands

```bash
cd backend && pytest            # Backend contract + integration tests (FakeGCPProvider — no cloud calls)
cd frontend && pytest           # Frontend integration tests
cd backend && ruff check .      # Lint backend
cd frontend && ruff check .     # Lint frontend
cd backend && uvicorn src.main:app --reload   # Run backend dev server
cd frontend && streamlit run src/app.py       # Run frontend dev server

# Opt-in manifest validation against a real Kubernetes API server using server-side dry-run.
# Requires a scratch kubeconfig; NEVER creates real resources (dry_run=["All"]).
LLMOPS_K8S_DRYRUN_KUBECONFIG=~/.kube/scratch-config \
  cd backend && pytest tests/dryrun
```

